  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Walking holidays for singles</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Feel a sense of freedom and independence like never before. Our walking holidays for singles are designed to help you experience the thrill of travelling solo. With exciting excursions and activities designed to embrace the local culture and customs, you’ll get to see what makes each destination so unique.</span></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093542/mountains.png?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/1a166e2fe2fa49be987ce731fd1d4fae" /></p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Why book a singles holiday to Europe with Inghams?</h2>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">Inghams singles holidays are designed to give you the perfect mix of activities, exploring and relaxation. We provide a wide range of group excursions and walking tours which are all optional, so you can dip in and out of group activities as you please.</p>
<p>Our single holidays will take you to the most beautiful destinations in Europe. See, explore, and discover incredible cities, amazing landscapes, and stunning coastlines. You certainly won't be short of options when it comes to planning your next solo adventure.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Friendly In Resort Reps</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13067604/otchamonix_gilleslansard.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b291af67f58548598b80b998074e22dc" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Relax and travel solo without feeling alone. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our hotels and resorts are full of friendly and experienced reps who can help with anything you need. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">They're a great resource for everything from reserving excursions to simply just having a friendly chat!</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Travel solo, your way </h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093778/travel-solo-your-way.png?width=165&amp;height=21" alt="solo walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/9963f3e50b644b21915f14bca19e712a" /></p>
<p>We have a number of excursions on offer directly through us, your hotel or the local tourist board.</p>
<p>Whether you want a walking holiday full of activities and adventures or simply want to relax by the lakeshore, our solo walking holidays offer the perfect balance of alone time and new discoveries.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>No single supplements </h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13093777/single-supplements.png?width=165&amp;height=21" alt="solo walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/6665bdb0b7dc4816a875f24b61025007" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Many of our hotels offer a supplement-free option for travelling solo, or solo-specific rooms where you'll be able to enjoy your holiday just like everyone else. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You'll also have the option to join group activities, make friends and take advantage of many other benefits exclusive to solo travellers.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Solo traveller hotels: Discover our favourite hotels for one</h2>
<p>Get away from it all, and have a holiday to remember. With our solo travellers in mind, we’ve selected some of the best hotels for people who like to travel alone. From Italy with its stunning lakeside views, to Austria and its majestic mountains, our single-friendly hotels are designed to make you feel at home, with plenty of things to do and see whilst you’re there. </p>
<div>
<p> </p>
<h3>Recommended hotels in Austria</h3>
</div>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt">Alpenhotel Kramerwirt</a>, Mayrhofen </strong></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms available with a low supplement</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13060113/mayrhofen.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/fae37c53744c474893fa0d209bc7cbac" /></strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This family run hotel offers exceptional hospitality, comfort and home-style cooking in an Austrian mountain setting. Wonderful walking opportunities are just outside your door, with the Naturpark walking programme.</p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/9ed9d1dc5645419e85115978c169b654" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9ed9d1dc5645419e85115978c169b654}" title="Bergresort Seefeld">Bergresort</a>, Seefeld</strong></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms available with a low supplement</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13060986/bergresort-seefeld-austria-exterior-with-outdoor-pool.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f573888c645b456eab95cc7f73890fc6" /></strong></p>
<p>The hotel is set in the heart of Seefeld, on the edge of the forest and next to the river. The hotel has a unique atmosphere, with a beautiful rustic interior. There are free walks at the hotel, plus a fun activity program and live music!</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/d0764a97320749fe824365958421503b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d0764a97320749fe824365958421503b}" title="Hotel Saalbacher Hof (Saalbach)">Hotel Saalbacherhof</a>, Saalbach </strong></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms available with a low supplement</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13060924/saalbach-7.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/28973fb7ecfe42b288e193677c0d461b" /></strong></p>
<p>The ideal choice for the solo traveller, this hotel is located just 50 metres from the Schattberg and Bernkogel gondolas, so you're perfectly situated to explore all that the resort has to offer. There's lots going on at this friendly hotel - with an activity programme, guided walks and yoga.</p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<h3>Recommended hotels in Switzerland</h3>
</div>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/af20be974a1d4650a55baed8aa139e30" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af20be974a1d4650a55baed8aa139e30}" title="Hotel Sunstar Grindelwald">Hotel Sunstar</a>, Grindelwald</strong></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms available with no supplement</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13057309/grindelwald.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/4653c53600b7417295c23bc22ef73b0e" /></strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This beautiful wellness hotel offers a range of treatments and activities, including indoor swimming. The ultimate place to stay for relaxation and wellbeing - so treat yourself to a bit of pampering!</p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/9bbad6e4beb54cb08acc713468bccbee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9bbad6e4beb54cb08acc713468bccbee}" title="Alpine Hotel Wengen">Alpine Hotel</a>, Wengen </strong></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms available with a low supplement</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100$; height: auto;" src="/media/13071774/alpine-hotel-wengen-switzerland-summer.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7aa0b51c21c549baa4d59c59523fa113" /></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The hotel’s location is ideal for guests. It's just a stone’s throw from the Männlichen cable cars and train station in Wengen, making it easy to get into town or hike up to Kleine Scheidegg.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f}" title="Hotel Alex">Hotel Alex</a>, Zermatt</strong></p>
<p><strong>Single rooms available with no supplement</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13080318/nw-exterior.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/3f0e192111184c51bc942687fe05d9ff" /></strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">Hotel Alex is in an elevated valley position, just off the main street in resort and only a few minutes walk to the Gornergrat railway and nearest lift. The hotel has a cheerful ambience, traditional design and it is superbly located for solo walkers.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div> </div>
<h3>Recommended hotels in Italy</h3>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/919b13aa1fae4bc68aa9503210e88b44" href="/{localLink:umb://document/919b13aa1fae4bc68aa9503210e88b44}" title="Hotel Adria">Hotel Adria</a>, Merano </strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><strong>Single deluxe rooms on allocation, low supplement</strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13076089/ita_mer_adri_ext-5.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9e4d27d52f7f4fbc8d9446d93c5f2546" /></strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This hotel offers free transfers to walking routes four times a week and provides maps, itineraries, and a 7-day Merano Mobilcard which offers free use of public buses, regional trains, and selected cable cars in the South Tyrol region.</p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3}" title="Hotel Rodella">Hotel Rodella</a>, Selva </strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><strong>Comfort twin room for sole use – in allocation</strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13076314/ita_selv_rode_01.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ade46e0498a94812a08016d7871f016f" /></strong></p>
<p>You’ll love the hotel’s Natura classification, which means it uses 100% green energy. It also has great facilities and offers a free daily packed lunch - ready and waiting for a day of walking in the mountains!</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/cde41f79cd114ef3bf06b1fc5876a3c1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cde41f79cd114ef3bf06b1fc5876a3c1}" title="Hotel Royal Village">Hotel Royal Village</a>, Limone</strong></p>
<p><strong>Standard rooms available for sole use – call to book</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13077394/royal-village-pool.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/8f51c88115cd43029a3abbcbcd0e3405" /></strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This hotel is located on a hill overlooking the lake and the surrounding mountains. Hotel has two outdoor pools and one indoor. Hotel also offers live music three times a week, great way to meet other guests and relax after a day of walking.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3>Recommended hotels in France</h3>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5}" title="Hotel La Folie Douce">La Folie Douce Hotel</a>, Chamonix</strong></p>
<p><strong>Standard rooms available with low supplement</strong></p>
<p><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13082623/la-folie-douce-hotel-chamonix-piscine.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/bb1e58750b0249c6a0a8be109dc63620" /></strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">La Folie Douce is a fantastic bed and breakfast option for the solo traveller. Located in Chamonix, this property provides easy access to all of the activities available in the town. A good option for solo travellers who wish to dine out in the evening.</p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"> </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac}" title="Hotel Champs Fleuris">Hotel Champs Fleuris</a>, Morzine </strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><strong> Classic Rooms for sole use, regular sized room, low supplement</strong></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><strong><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13092177/champs-fleuris-6.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/8cfe9dc2cdc34913bd9aacdef07190c2" /></strong></p>
<p>This hotel offers lots of facilities to make your stay enjoyable - 2 free walks every week, plus spa and wellness facilities, fitness room, tennis courts and games room make this a great choice. Guests also receive a discounted resort card good for free lift rides and access to local attractions.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Book your solo holiday</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Book your independent solo holiday today! Solo holidays are a great way to just do what you want, when you want. Don’t miss the opportunity to explore your own interests and create memories that last a lifetime.</span></p>
<p><strong>Book online or call us on <span class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</span> or book online.</strong></p>
